/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7aeed31fd1fb09e5faa21bd825e6bf9b269c2b","tid":1332182,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"因為連登仔逢反必升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逢撐必跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下隻2662 停埋牌就知咩事啦，碌柒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3486870208feb0567fd04ef96e16a0be38bdc3ed","tid":1332182,"uid":90180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"我唸全香港都冇股評人夠膽話受惠150單程證，<br />\n每日150穩定輸入，<br />\n穩賺不賠。<br />\n係呢道細細聲提連登仔，<br />\n唔好比出面d人知。"},{"pid":"d74a7cd46d93f1b016514f644095ed44eae250e4","tid":1332182,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2365000/2368013/88779_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2365000%2F2368013%2F88779_600.png&h=00a87de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2368013%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=b2213ee7\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">陳永堅</span>也指香港方面，現在<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人用煤氣已愈來愈少</span>，「以前一戶有3人，現在一戶只有2.5個人，人口少了，每個家庭簡單了，在家煮食要求又低了，洗澡會在家吃飯未必，好多人出街食，尤其住在納米樓的，<span style=\"color: red;\">基本上沒有廚房</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n他也坦言，<span style=\"color: red;\">煤氣跟電力的競爭很大</span>，「一條煤氣喉來到你家，入到廚房，是否代表你煮食會全用到煤氣？實際上並不如此，如你煲飯會用電飯煲，我相信有99%的香港人也用電飯煲煲飯，你煲湯很多時用電子瓦罉、壓力煲等，你早餐吃的多士也是用多士爐製作，也是用電的；以往用水煲煲水，現在大家也普遍改用電水煲，70年代後也出現了微波爐，其後也有電磁爐的出現，<span style=\"color: red;\">因此電力取了我們很多的市場</span>，電力跟我們有很大競爭。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">煤氣冇人用</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ccd3bb00b292b6bc5a04c7a51b82f49ea994fccd","tid":1332182,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"冇人用嫁啦"},{"pid":"53530803eaa45b0266c38db3bf4332fa59a8ab31","tid":1332182,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">😏擋房用閪到煤氣咩</span>"},{"pid":"97acb90796f6eb29d72e160f970685b8b757bf0e","tid":1332182,"uid":249207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1835c6eca44245553adc96db38d47f2f310272","tid":1332182,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dfa9303b6cf5a3a31f1edd08e3604da66841224","tid":1332182,"uid":44722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b44a1b40605480f5e65e3953afcefd27d881add6","tid":1332182,"uid":35930,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"ba0080fd400228a151d1d9f5dc51c46abe4e3096","tid":1332182,"uid":54481,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"錯！<br />\n<br />\n煤氣我唔識，但係領展係因為&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2871826/org/09ee69298bee3f1e4b485366bd23f9b6.jpg/pZ797V-U-m7NohL5rjlvRyNMngVj20Y6bnadPW52nT0?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2871826%2Forg%2F09ee69298bee3f1e4b485366bd23f9b6.jpg%2FpZ797V-U-m7NohL5rjlvRyNMngVj20Y6bnadPW52nT0%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=9d79284c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"師兄 未免太唔了解師父佢老人家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXPCPwk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb